h2(style="color:crimson;") Historial
if productos.length > 0
    div(class="table-responsive")
        table(class="table table-dark")
            tr 
                th(class='text-center text-light') ID
                th(class='text-center text-light') Nombre 
                th(class='text-center text-light') Precio 
each producto in productos 
    tr
        td(class='text-center text-light')= producto.nombre
        td(class='text-center text-light')= producto.price
    else if productos.length == 0
        h3(class="alert alert-danger") no se encontraron datos